---
import '../styles/global.css';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="en">
<head>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
  <title>Microsoft License Services & Partnerships | Sky States</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Explore how Microsoft License Services play a pivotal role in building institutional partnerships, delivering official certifications, and empowering career readiness." name="description"/>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://skystates.us/microsoft-partnership" />
  
  

  <style>
    .material-symbols-outlined {
      font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
    }
    .upward-gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(to top, #ffffff 0%, #eef5fa 100%);
    }
    .accent-card {
      border-left: 4px solid #005d90;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background font-body-md text-on-surface">
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative w-full pt-20 pb-24 overflow-hidden upward-gradient">
      <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 items-center gap-gutter relative z-10">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container text-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Enterprise &amp; Licensing</span>
          <h1 class="font-headline-xl text-5xl md:text-6xl text-primary font-extrabold leading-tight">
            The Role of Microsoft License Services
          </h1>
          <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            How official licensing, voucher distribution, and cloud service integration drive educational excellence and institutional partnerships at Sky States.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden md:block relative h-[400px]">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/40 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_30px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] border border-outline-variant/20 flex items-center justify-center p-8">
            <div class="text-center space-y-4">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[96px] text-primary">analytics</span>
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface">Authorized Curriculum</div>
              <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant max-w-xs">Verifiable exam vouchers and cloud tenant access powered by official license frameworks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Sections -->
    <section class="max-w-[1024px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop py-20 space-y-16">
      <!-- Intro Card -->
      <div class="accent-card bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-r-3xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/30">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Building Bridges with Microsoft Licensing</h2>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-4">
          In today's digital economy, cloud competencies are no longer optional. They are the bedrock of modern enterprise engineering. At Sky States, our mission is to deliver career-ready talents in Cloud Architecture, Cybersecurity, and Artificial Intelligence. 
        </p>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          To achieve this, we leverage official <strong>Microsoft License Services</strong> to provision sandboxed learning environments, distribute authorized exam vouchers (DP-900, SC-900, AZ-900), and build strong co-learning frameworks that connect academic training with industry standards.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Grid of Key Pillars -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 space-y-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">vpn_key</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-on-surface">Authorized Voucher Access</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Direct provisioning of official Microsoft certification vouchers. Our licensed distribution ensures that every eligible student receives validated credentials upon completing coursework.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 space-y-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">cloud_queue</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-on-surface">Sandboxed Lab Tenants</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            By utilising enterprise-level Microsoft cloud licenses, we provide students with hands-on environments to configure Azure Active Directory, deploy Kubernetes, and run security audits safely.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 space-y-4">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">handshake</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-on-surface">Institutional Partnership</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            Licensing agreements establish a formal bridge between our curriculum and official Microsoft learning pathways, giving clients and corporate partners full trust in our graduates.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Detailed Breakdown -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-on-surface text-center md:text-left">Strategic Licensing Operations</h3>
        
        <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/3">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary">Curriculum Alignment</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3">
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
              Our training materials are designed around official Microsoft Learn objectives. By integrating Microsoft License Services, we ensure that students are not just learning theoretical concepts, but are working with the actual software versions and Azure cloud portal experiences demanded by global employers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/3">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary">Enterprise Validation</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3">
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
              For corporate clients seeking to upskill their engineering cohorts, our licensed delivery model guarantees that training meets compliance benchmarks. We handle the provisioning of software licenses, tracking student progress, and administering certifications under authorized guidelines.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/20 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
          <div class="md:w-1/3">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary">Secure Infrastructure</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="md:w-2/3">
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
              All learning platforms and lab resources are secured using official Microsoft authentication mechanisms. This guarantees data privacy for both individual students and corporate clients, creating a trusted portal for career development.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
